sexp_memory.h \- Wrappers around basic memory allocation/deallocation routines to allow memory usage limiting\&. Only enabled if \fISEXP_LIMIT_MEMORY\fP is defined when building the library, otherwise the routines are defined to be the standard malloc/calloc/realloc/free functions\&.  

